# Git-tracked deployment settings for this app.
# During an explicit deploy flow, push changes here when you want the server
# cron deploy to pick them up.
#
# Keep machine-specific and secret values out of this file. Those stay in the
# live .env that the installer creates on the server.
#
# Leave this as auto for hosted/student workspaces. Hosted workers should use
# deploy/app-shell.txt for shell intent because they may be denied *.env edits.
# For non-hosted deploy flows, this env-style value may still be set to text or
# graphical when the deployment should force one shell.

GIZMOAPP_SHELL=auto
